  "ciliary_role": "Mutations cause syndromic short stature, skeletal abnormalities, and cataracts associated with ciliary dysfunction (31034465). Critical for the formation of cilia and for receptor mediated endocytosis. Promotes the activation and pericentriolar localisation of Rab11+ vesicles, triggers the Rab8- dependent pathway and translocation of Smo to the primary cilium. Controls the production of PtdIns3P at the endocytic recycling compartment located at the base of the primary cilium (24697898). PI3KC2伪- dependent and VPS34- independent generation of PI3P controls primary cilium- mediated autophagy in response to shear stress (31941925).",
